09:56.978 --> 10:02.766
met the environmental movement, there were a 
whole lot of people who said we frightened the

09:56.978 --> 10:02.766
birds on Heligoland. Heligoland was some kind of 
bird sanctuary. So we took a cinema film. of the

10:07.598 --> 10:08.559
operation. And when we let off the 6,000 tons on the 
