10:16.672 --> 10:19.856
all got up and they circled around for about a 
quarter of an hour and sat down again. And that's

10:20.297 --> 10:22.020
all that happened. Well anyway, I had a graduate 
student looking after this and it was very

10:23.382 --> 10:34.017
interesting seeing Germany immediately after 
the defeat. You know, the complete collapse of

10:36.725 --> 10:40.891
their view of themselves as the heron folk. None of 
them knew what to do or what they wanted to do, and

10:42.293 --> 10:46.439
they just waited to be told. And I remember I had 
meetings, I went to the

