12:42.924 --> 12:45.647
produced a key from his pocket and opened it. I 
walked in, completely empty hut, nothing

12:46.548 --> 12:52.774
whatever there, except a little table against one 
wall. a vase of fresh flowers on it, and a picture of

12:53.193 --> 12:58.380
some Nazi tough over it. They'd made a little 
shrine there. And imagine the stupidity of taking

13:00.622 --> 13:05.889
me out there on the off chance that I wouldn't smell 
