14:28.392 --> 14:33.196
have a typist half time, I felt this was not 
reasonable. And that afternoon, a man came in who

14:33.236 --> 14:46.827
asked me whether I would take a job in Canada as head 
of the physics department in Canada. Well, this

14:47.028 --> 14:49.870
was the largest physics department in the British 
Empire and Obviously a prestigious job with a very

14:50.187 --> 14:55.713
good pay, paid $10,000 a year, which is a lot of 
money in those days. And so I took this job. I knew I

14:59.117 --> 15:02.801
didn't want it, and I knew I wasn't going to like it. 
