15:03.802 --> 15:08.487
this typist that I took the job. And I went out to 
Canada, my wife and four children. And my wife took

15:13.312 --> 15:17.697
an enormous dislike to Canada and wouldn't stay 
there. And I rather wanted to get out too. I think,

15:21.011 --> 15:26.276
in other circumstances, if my wife hadn't 
disliked it, I'd probably have stayed. I don't

15:26.336 --> 15:27.017
know. I think I'd probably come down here because I 
