15:45.453 --> 15:51.179
saw President Sproul and recommended Ravel. And 
there was a good deal of opposition to Ravel down

15:51.499 --> 15:54.082
here. And I told him to overrule it and then the 
locals would settle down and make Ravel

15:54.723 --> 15:59.908
directives. He did. Well, anyway, so I had this 
short time in Canada. And during that time in

16:05.294 --> 16:08.998
