17:13.304 --> 17:18.310
think about the origin of the Earth's magnetic 
field. I'd started to think about it just before I

17:18.571 --> 17:20.954
left England. I did a lot of work on that while I was 
in Canada and while I was down here. And in

17:25.740 --> 17:35.833
